Class JohnnyMoves

  • java.lang.Object
    • JohnnyMoves

  • public class JohnnyMoves
extends java.lang.Object
    The JohnnyMoves Class represents a JohnnyMoves object that has an Arraylist of Items, Parcels, and Trackers. The JohnnyMoves object can add and remove Items from the queue, as well as add and search trackers on the Parcels. The object can also generate A transaction report for the day based on the transactions made. The object can also check for Parcels available for the items in queue.
